OL,5, An estimated 700,000 children are being
OL,6, taught in unsafe or ageing school      
OL,7, buildings in England that need major   
OL,8, repairs, according to a report.        
OL,10,FThe National Audit Office (NAO) report 
OL,11,Fsays the Department for Education (DfE)
OL,12,Fhas, since 2021, assessed the risk of  
OL,13,Finjury or death from a school building 
OL,14,Fcollapse as "very likely and critical".
OL,16,FTeachers have told the BBC about risks 
OL,17,Fposed by sewage leaks and asbestos.    
OL,19,FThe DfE says it has been "significantly
OL,20,Finvesting in transforming schools".    
